{"tid":1248010,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"請大家同上一輩解釋：點解要戴口罩同埋遮鏡頭","createTime":"2019-06-21T10:17:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-21T19:29:09.000Z","uid":39752,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0695f07385b4b215a41f667419a0308190d3d2c7","tid":1248010,"uid":39752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T10:17:49.000Z","msg":"啱啱睇過facebook，好多星期日有出嚟而上咗年紀（&gt; 40）嘅人唔知道點解要遮鏡頭<br />\n佢哋觀感上覺得要遮鏡頭已經踩到「破壞公物」條線<br />\n即使膠紙同遮都無破壞到任何嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申唔係覺得要收手防止落人口實乜乜乜（根本要入你點都入到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n但好多上一輩係唔知道<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">出嚟行影到樣</span></strong>已經有危險<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">大家可以用以下論點去同長輩解釋：</span></strong><br />\n1. 某個地方係唔係暴動係隨口噏，就算所有人和平企喺度都會被屈，睇吓政府連日嚟對612係咪暴動都無固定答案<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2. 只要警方話某個地方有暴動，你就算路過都有機會中暴動罪，無人知612因暴動被拘捕嘅人係唔係純粹企得太前唔好彩被捉到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3. 由警方亂咁開槍同射催淚彈已經知，佢哋根本無意分辨和平定係暴力，而係全部當暴徒處理，「和平集會就唔會被拉」係大話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n4. 所以就算係和平集會都要遮鏡頭，警察同成個政府都唔可信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n5. 如果啲人係想破壞公物，扑爛個鏡頭重快啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他內容請大家自由發揮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />記得要有耐性唔好將自己人推向另一邊<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">不論係和理非定係勇武，一定要知道被影到樣有幾危險</span></strong><br />\n今日唔盡快教識所有自己人，第時大家都係會一鑊熟，老人家死咗唔知咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ceb2a3803ab139a7773f0da57195576d8c8c3428","tid":1248010,"uid":49336,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T10:18:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/video/20141002/720pix/1412195409_ce6f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fvideo%2F20141002%2F720pix%2F1412195409_ce6f.jpg&h=36d7e2c0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ba4fd05a15f7232fb81623b497c2262713880779","tid":1248010,"uid":39752,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ceb2a3803ab139a7773f0da57195576d8c8c3428","tid":1248010,"uid":49336,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T10:18:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/video/20141002/720pix/1412195409_ce6f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fvideo%2F20141002%2F720pix%2F1412195409_ce6f.jpg&h=36d7e2c0&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T10:19:02.000Z","msg":"你有無撚睇我寫咗咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4108d34fa478b414c85bc7ff5bf82dd7613751c","tid":1248010,"uid":39752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T10:21:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31a0ef8c0c912c2f7946e01c84fc6506fdc54730","tid":1248010,"uid":39752,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T10:25:13.000Z","msg":"一時又話標題寫清楚要做乜<br />\n寫完啲撚樣咪又係唔撚睇內文就自由想像<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b52d3db5bc3357ac8720b61372203bf3135482e","tid":1248010,"uid":39752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T10:32:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b53e76fae766b9f735f0351cfaebc2c59986b081","tid":1248010,"uid":39752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T10:38:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"754a2814465a3e3b06a6ed58d8c3db310ee24e45","tid":1248010,"uid":39752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T10:43:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/ass